title: Meris
---

The Pretty Meris is a female member of the Windblown. Despite being known as Pretty Meris, there is nothing pretty about her inside or out. She is near 6 foot tall and has blond hair, she is earless, with a slit nose and scars crossing both her cheeks. She is said to have cold dead eyes.. She dresses all in mail. There is talk that underneath her shirt only scars are left by the men who'd cut off her breasts.

She is originally from Westeros and eventually joined the Windblown and serves as the company Torturer. I


